{"tid":992582,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[考的士牌] 有冇人熟D 試題?","createTime":"2019-01-23T09:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T07:55:10.000Z","uid":79410,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9ac082bcc39a093b68349222f6f37c88f33c8f","tid":992582,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"下個星期考的士牌. 咁我報咗李健個D 堂. <br />\n發覺佢D 模擬試題好似好多bug. <br />\n例如: 司機執到嘢, A) 要6小時內交去警署 B) 要6小時內交去警署及存放 答案: 係B. 有存放字眼<br />\n但係第另外一題, 只有 要6小時內交去警署, 冇&quot;存放&quot;字眼. <br />\n但我睇返的士則例簡介. 成句嘢就冇&quot;存放&quot; , 只係交去警署就得. <br />\n<br />\n另外: 又問司機可以拒絕咩人上車? A) 未包好既貨物 B) 傳染病 答案係B<br />\n但係成本的士則例又冇話可以拒絕傳染病人坐車, 但就講明貨物必須包好. 我唔明點解佢個模擬試係傳染病人<br />\n<br />\n想問下真實考試, D 試題有冇咁唔清唔楚? 有冇D 好D 既模擬試做下?"},{"pid":"ff8f262e87d30d9324eecbfc8403b2ea55e55b0c","tid":992582,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"模擬筆試應該都係港駕最正常...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hksm.com.hk/written-test/taxi/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhksm.com.hk%2Fwritten-test%2Ftaxi%2Fchi%2F&d=B443tWVhrLE9WEntoKY0GU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e9ad045a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hksm.com.hk/written-test/taxi/chi/</a>"},{"pid":"622a0c199bfa7f364aa471a77f3a82ebcf23dde5","tid":992582,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ff8f262e87d30d9324eecbfc8403b2ea55e55b0c","tid":992582,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T09:48:16.000Z","msg":"模擬筆試應該都係港駕最正常...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hksm.com.hk/written-test/taxi/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhksm.com.hk%2Fwritten-test%2Ftaxi%2Fchi%2F&d=B443tWVhrLE9WEntoKY0GU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e9ad045a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hksm.com.hk/written-test/taxi/chi/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T10:05:54.000Z","msg":"唔該先. 呢個我都有做過. <br />\n不過我嫌佢每次做得20題. <br />\n不過我都覺得駕院D 題好過李健好多. 李健D 題真係1999. 好影響對睇書既記憶."},{"pid":"2